text: Eugen Fürstenberger (12 February 1880 - February 1975) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1975 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bas- Rhin
